* Complete documents (wikis on github)
* Intercept getaddrinfo()/freeaddrinfo() calls in zfor client
* Allow zfor client set target host
* Export client setting functions to zfor php extension
* Change host-list implementation to reflect host-list modification to virtual host addresses in time, instead of update while the virtual host config changes
* Allow user to select HTTP method used for detecting host aliveness, because some home-made web services DO NOT support the default HTTP HEAD method

